    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Caterpillar, pupa and adult of Gamia shelleyi, collected on Dracaena camerooniana, Ebogo, Cameroon [SCC]. 1 – 2, early final instar, dorsal view; 3 – 6 late final instar, 3 – 4 dorsal view, 5, anterodorsal view, 6 anterior view; 7 – 9 pupa in near dorsal view, dorsolateral view and lateral view; 10, adult female underside, 9 Oct 2005." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/253537/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

